  <brief_title>Absolute Bioavailability of YH4808 With Accelerator Mass Spectrometry(AMS)-Based Microdose Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study to Determine the Absolute Bioavailability of YH4808 Using Simultaneous Oral Therapeutic- and [14C]-Labeled Intravenous Microdoses</official_title>
